📌 Project Description:
The Love Emoji Quiz is an interactive web-based quiz game that challenges users to guess the correct meaning of love-related emojis.
The game presents multiple-choice options and provides instant feedback on the user's selection.

🚀 Features

🎨 User-friendly interface with attractive emoji-based questions.

✅ Instant feedback with color-coded results.

🔁 Retry option to attempt the quiz multiple times.

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML - Structure of the quiz.

CSS - Styling and visual design.

JavaScript - Logic and interactivity.

🎮 How to Play

Open index.html in a web browser.

Read the question and select an answer from the options.

Get instant feedback on your choice.

